ww.theverge.com/23507492/sonos-best-speaker-one-roam-move- Five-arc-beam-ray-sub&quot;}, {“title”：“Sonos首席执行官表示旧应用程序无法重新发布”，“url”：“https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/20/24224754/sonos-ceo-old-s2- app-re-release-cant-be&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;这是 Sonos 的下一个旗舰条形音箱&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24195947/ sonos-lasso-soundbar-photos-features-leak&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;ju21o3&quot;>;Era 100 是 Sonos 连接 Wi 的简单推荐-Fi 扬声器，无论您想将其放在家里的哪个位置。它足够紧凑，适合大多数地方，但提供强劲的音量和优质的声音，让您的音乐有一定的深度，而又不会变得太低音。另一方面，Move 2 有点像 Era 100...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/24/24226829/ sonos-era-100-move-2-smart-speaker-apple-pencil-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/24/24226829/sonos-era-100-move-2-smart-speaker-apple-pencil-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/24/24226829/sonos-era-100-move-2-smart-speaker-apple-pencil-deal-sale</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-24T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-24T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>如果没有我的眼镜，Shokz OpenFit Air 就更完美了</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;有人在箱子里拿出 Shokz OpenFit Air。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/OoTBB5-vrkVwfrd90wMSZokllXs=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73541393/247218_shokz_fitness_buds_AKrales_0141 .0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Shokz OpenFit Air 是一对使用空气传导的轻量级开耳式耳机。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;低音非常适合开耳式耳机健身耳机，可惜我的眼镜阻碍了耳挂设计。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24221155/shokz-openfit-air-open-earbuds-fitness-可穿戴设备&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24221155/shokz-openfit-air-open-earbuds-fitness-wearables" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24221155/shokz-openfit-air-open-earbuds-fitness-wearables</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-23T19:00:54-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-23T19:00:54-04:00</updated><title> Valve 正式宣布 Deadlock，一款“处于早期开发阶段”的游戏</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/1HSB_SV7P0DLLsyfmWSaxoWdKiw=/16x0:2977x1974/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73540783 /deadlock.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;OHis6v&quot;>;Valve 最终以可以想象到的最简单的方式正式宣布&lt;em>;死锁&lt;/em>;。该游戏&lt;a href=&quot;https://store.steampowered.com/app/1422450/Deadlock/&quot;>;现在有一个 Steam 页面&lt;/a>;，其中列出了 Valve 为其开发商和发行商，以及一个简单的通知：&lt;/ p>; &lt;blockquote>;&lt;p id=&quot;D9RMpq&quot;>;Deadlock 处于早期开发阶段，有大量临时艺术和实验性游戏玩法。目前访问权限仅限于通过我们的游戏测试人员邀请的好友。&lt;/p>;&lt;/blockquote>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;Q5DJNQ&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem- component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;我们玩了 Valve 的秘密新射击游戏 Deadlock&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2024/8/12/24219016/valve-deadlock-hands-on-secret-new-game&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;6y07MX&quot;>;Valve 提供没有其他细节，只是一个动画预告片。 （您可以在上面看到它的静态屏幕截图。）系统要求仅提到游戏需要 64 位处理器和操作系统。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Wh3Y8i&quot;>;虽然游戏表面上是一个秘密到目前为止，有关此事的细节已经流传了几个月。信息开始&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.eurogamer.net/images-leak-of-valves-next-game-and-its-an-overwatch-style-hero-shooter&quot;>;从封闭的游戏测试中出现&lt; /a>; 五月。到八月，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.eurogamer.net/valve-hero-shooter-deadlock-still-hasnt-been-announced-but-had-16k-steam-concurrent-players-this-weekend&quot; >;数十...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/23/24219054/valve-deadlock-announcement&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/23/24219054/valve-deadlock-announcement" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/23/24219054/valve-deadlock-announcement</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry></feed>